{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"72aba00e11","title":"对卫立煌《告台湾袍泽朋友书》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"be00a861cf","index":0,"year":1955,"month":3,"day":13,"articleId":"72aba00e11"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"a950e9e631","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"卫立煌，原国民党军将领，解放战争后期，担任国民党军东北“剩总”总司令，因没有积极执行蒋介石的作战命令，被软禁于南京。1949年1月蒋介石引退后卫去香港，1955年3月回国，并发表了《告台湾袍泽朋友书》，全文载《人民日报》和香港《文汇报》"},{"id":"42d7401d45","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。朱，指朱德。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"61a06de311","type":"title","text":"对卫立煌《告台湾袍泽朋友书》“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11"},{"id":"a950e9e631","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、朱、邓（请小平办）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11"},{"id":"42d7401d45","type":"paragraph","text":"此件以一字不改，照原文待卫到广州时即行发表为好。在广州发表时，即送香港登报，并登广州报纸。同时由新华社发来北京，播发北京及全国登报，并发口语广播，译成外文发表。此件完全可用，不须要修改。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11"},{"id":"64edc46d8a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11"},{"id":"eb23abbc5a","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11"}],"page":{"id":"e68ac7ea78","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"72aba00e11","start":490,"end":490}}}},"__N_SSG":true}